OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780074357
OL,3,CLorry driver dies after HGV crashes
OL,4,Cinto house
OL,6,FA lorry driver has died after a HGV
OL,7,Fcrashed into a house.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,10,Fjunction of Church Road and Chapel
OL,11,FLane in Banks, Lancashire, at 7.27am
OL,12,Fon 28 May following reports that a
OL,13,Fheavy goods vehicle had collided with
OL,14,Fa property.
OL,16,FLancashire Police has now confirmed
OL,17,Fthe driver, a man in his 50s, died at
OL,18,Fthe scene. His death is not being
OL,19,Ftreated as suspicious.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
