OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780074357
OL,3,CLorry driver dies after HGV crashes
OL,4,Cinto house
OL,6,FA force spokesperson said: "At 7:27am
OL,7,Fon Thursday 28th May we were called to
OL,8,Freports of a single vehicle collision
OL,9,Fon Long Lane, Banks.
OL,11,F"It was reported that a HGV collided
OL,12,Fwith a house. No one inside the house
OL,13,Fsuffered any injuries.
OL,15,F"Emergency services attended and, very
OL,16,Fsadly, despite the best efforts of
OL,17,Femergency services a man in his 50s
OL,18,Fdied at the scene. His death is not
OL,19,Fbeing treated as suspicious, and a
OL,20,Ffile will be passed to the coroner in
OL,21,Fdue course.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
