CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780074357
OL,3,CLorry driver dies after HGV crashes
OL,4,Cinto house
OL,6,F"If you witnessed this incident, have
OL,7,Fany CCTV/dashcam/doorbell footage,
OL,8,Fplease call 101 quoting log 318 of
OL,9,F28th May."
OL,11,FA Lancashire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,12,Fspokesperson added: "At 07.28am on May
OL,13,F28 2026, four fire engines from
OL,14,FTarleton, Chorley, Bamber Bridge and
OL,15,FSouthport, along with the Urban Search
OL,16,Fand Rescue team from Lancashire Fire
OL,17,Fand Rescue Service attended to a road
OL,18,Ftraffic collision involving a large
OL,19,Fvehicle and a building. Crews remain
OL,20,Fin attendance."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
